  "description": "Natural adhesives (hide glue, casein, starch paste, birch tar), synthetic adhesives (phenolic resin, epoxy, cyanoacrylate, silicone RTV, UV-cure), semiconductor-specific adhesives (epoxy molding compounds, die attach films), and metal coating processes (anodizing). Spans stone-age birch tar hafting to semiconductor encapsulation — adhesive technology connects every era of industrial development.",
